late your strategy and are they empowered to execute on it?</strong>\n\nSince Consulting WP\'s founding in 1985, strategy has been our core business. We work with companies in every industry to develop strategies that deliver results.[/vc_wp_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'VC Right Blog Sidebar', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'vc-right-blog-sidebar', '', '', '2016-01-13 04:38:07', '2016-01-13 04:38:07', '', 0, 'http://consulting.stylemixthemes.com/?post_type=stm_vc_sidebar&amp;p=527', 0, 'stm_vc_sidebar', '', 0),
